{"tid":1616541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴黎警局被持刀漢闖入施襲　據報四名警員死亡","createTime":"2019-10-03T12:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:51:22.000Z","uid":98777,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e26a17d57ebd968f5c5f9e046bd28fb413f00ff4","tid":1616541,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎警察總局被一名持刀男人闖入施襲，消息說，四名警員死亡，這名男子其後被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報道，行兇男子是警局的員工，但未知工種。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期四下午約一時，警局事後被封鎖，多部緊急車輛停在外面，警局旁邊的一個地鐵站亦關閉。<br />\n<br />\n原定今日訪問土耳其的內政部長卡斯塔內押後行程，趕到警局視察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=9c27b3e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm&h=23a72608\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3b54144cdb4e5845bb4eb7fd61182aef971b7490","tid":1616541,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"74c8f62a9f9e0e06f36eecac0d08b90317c733bc","tid":1616541,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88287a706dd19bc9616bc51e19e7b8843545ceac","tid":1616541,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"push"}]}